        <title>adding_an_api</title>
        <link>https://conze.pt/guide/adding_an_api?rev=1643373860&amp;do=diff</link>
        <description>adding an API
API
The easiest way to add an API is to copy a similar API-fetching file from “app/explore2/src/fetch” and then making the necessary changes to it.

For some APIs you might want to render zoomable IIIF images, for others you may just want a link to the webpage.</description>
